      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "### Initial Release - Markr\r\n\r\n  Priority markers - three built-in triggers, always available:\r\n  - `!`  Important\r\n  - `!!`  Urgent\r\n  - `!!!`  Critical\r\n\r\n  Custom markers :configurable 1–3 character trigger, label, Lucide icon, line tint,\r\n  and badge color.\r\n\r\n  Live Preview & Reading View:  both surfaces render identically. Priority markers stay\r\n  type-editable in the editor; icon markers reveal the raw trigger when the cursor is on\r\n   the line.\r\n\r\n  Commands: apply, remove, and cycle priority markers from the command palette.\r\n\r\n  Theme-compatible: oklch tints composite over any theme background. Style Settings\r\n  support for radius, padding, and color customization.",
